   PAGE BODY
   ============================================================ #}
<div class="home-body">
    <div class="container">

        <p>At Cathcart United Free Church we believe that faith is lived out together.
        We are a warm and welcoming congregation and we love spending time together —
        not just on Sundays but throughout the week.</p>
        <p>Whether you are looking for a relaxed social gathering, an opportunity to
        explore faith questions, or ways to get involved in the wider community, here
        you will find the many ways our congregation connects, serves and grows — both
        within our own church family and alongside our neighbours in the wider Cathcart
        community.</p>

        {# ── OFF THE CUF NOTICE CARD ── #}
        <div class="notice-card" role="note">
            <span class="notice-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🎉</span>
            <div class="notice-card-body">
                <h3>Off the CUF</h3>
                <p>Our own monthly gathering — food, friendship and faith on the first
                Saturday of every month, 10:30am&ndash;12pm. Everyone welcome.
                <a href="/life/off-the-cuf/" class="section-link">Find out more &rarr;</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        {# ── FELLOWSHIP GROUPS + PRAYER GARDEN ── #}
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="section-heading-icon" aria-hidden="true">👋</span>
            <h2>Fellowship &amp; Rest</h2>
            <span class="section-heading-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-panels feature-panels--two">
            <div class="feature-panel feature-panel--left">
                <span class="feature-panel-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏠</span>
                <h3>Fellowship Groups</h3>
                <p class="p-tight"><strong>Home Groups</strong> &mdash; small groups
                with members from Cathcart UF and Cathcart Church of Scotland meet
                regularly to look at the Bible together, pray and chat. Days and
                times vary by group.</p>
                <p>We also run additional groups from time to time, including
                Christianity Explored, Discipleship Explored and Talking Jesus.</p>
                <a href="/contact/" class="section-link">Ask about a group &rarr;</a>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-panel feature-panel--left">
                <span class="feature-panel-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌳</span>
                <h3>Prayer Garden</h3>
                <div class="photo-row">
                    <div class="photo-placeholder">
                        <img src="/assets/images/prayergarden1.jpg" alt="Cathcart UF prayer garden" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="photo-placeholder">
                        <img src="/assets/images/prayergarden2.jpg" alt="Cathcart UF prayer garden" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="photo-placeholder">
                        <img src="/assets/images/prayergarden3.jpg" alt="Cathcart UF prayer garden" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>A quiet space for all to rest. Have a walk around, sit a while, and
                enjoy a bit of quiet time. We have seasonal topics on display for
                contemplation and prayer — we hope you'll find the garden a helpful
                place.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        {# ── QUIET SPACES + MOMENTS CAFE ── #}
        <div class="feature-panels feature-panels--two">
            <div class="feature-panel feature-panel--left">
                <span class="feature-panel-icon" aria-hidden="true">🕊️</span>
                <h3>Quiet Spaces</h3>
                <p>Two opportunities each week to step away from the busyness of life
                and find a moment of stillness and peace.</p>
                <p class="p-tight"><strong>Rest &amp; Restore</strong><br />
                Mondays, 9&ndash;10am &mdash; Cathcart Baptist Church<br />
                Rest and pray within the sanctuary, stay for a short time or longer.</p>
                <p><strong>Quiet Space</strong><br />
                Tuesdays, 10&ndash;11am &mdash; Cathcart Church of Scotland<br />
                A time of reflection, simplicity and stillness.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-panel feature-panel--left">
                <span class="feature-panel-icon" aria-hidden="true">☕</span>
                <h3>Moments Café</h3>
                <p>A dementia friendly café &mdash; all welcome! A warm and relaxed
                space for everyone in the community.</p>
                <p><strong>1st and 3rd Monday of the month, 2&ndash;3:30pm</strong><br />
                Cathcart Church of Scotland</p>
            </div>
        </div>

