        <p>Cathcart United Free Church is part of the United Free Church of Scotland.
        We have a number of sister congregations in the Glasgow area with whom we
        share fellowship and friendship.</p>

        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.croftfootuf.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Croftfoot United Free Church</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://darnleychurch.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Darnley United Free Church</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.ufcos.org.uk/congregations/shieldhall/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shieldhall &amp; Drumoyne United Free Church</a></li>
        </ul>

        <p>Cathcart UF is part of the wider United Free Church of Scotland
        denomination. For information about the national work of our denomination
        visit <a href="https://www.ufcos.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ufcos.org.uk</a>.</p>

